 coalesce at the isotropic point (\\Delta=1) and edge-locking\nbecomes stable in the whole \\Delta>1 region.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Jun 2013 21:57:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 7 Jul 2013 16:22:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 23 Dec 2013 12:34:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-12-24"}
