act\nHausdorff spaces are homeomorphic if, and only if, the lattices of continuous\n[0, 1]-valued functions on the spaces are isomorphic.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Jun 2013 14:36:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 25 Jun 2013 16:09:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 10 Jun 2014 09:09:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-15"}
