phy admittance and correlation spectra, and\nearthquake moment-depth release are interpreted in light of this hypothetical\nstructure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Jun 2013 16:59:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-06-17"}
